the project dependacies:
1- OpenMesh: the half-edge datastructure used to describe 3D surfaces http://openmesh.org/ 
2- OpenSceneGraph: a scene graph management library http://www.openscenegraph.org/
3- Qt 5.7 https://www.qt.io/

the project is now using Qt Creator but I plan to use CMake in the future

for any info please contact me ahmedabdelhay6339@gmail.com


